RESOURCE.name: CDS/VII/275/glade1 by MOC
RESOURCE.DESCRIPTION: CDS/VII/275/glade1 by MOC object selection from Aladin

FIELD.name: _RAJ2000
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Right ascension (FK5, Equinox=J2000.0) (computed by VizieR, not part of the original data. The format may include more digits than the original data because of internal accuracy requirements in VizieR and across other CDS services)

FIELD.name: _DEJ2000
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Declination (FK5, Equinox=J2000.0) (computed by VizieR, not part of the original data. The format may include more digits than the original data because of internal accuracy requirements in VizieR and across other CDS services)

FIELD.name: Bmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Apparent B magnitude (predicted if Flag = 2 or 4)

FIELD.name: modzHyp
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? HyperLEDA redshift distance modulus (modz=5log(DL)+25, where DL is the luminosity distance in Mpc) (1)

FIELD.name: logd25Hyp
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? HyperLEDA decimal logarithm of the length of the projected major axis of a galaxy at the isophotal level 25mag/arcsec^2^ in the B-band

FIELD.name: logr25Hyp
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? HyperLEDA decimal logarithm of major axis / minor axis ratio

FIELD.name: logdcHyp
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? HyperLEDA decimal logarithm of apparent corrected diameter

FIELD.name: PAHyp
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? HyperLEDA Position angle (from north through east)

FIELD.name: U-BHypC
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? HyperLEDA total apparent corrected U-B colour index

FIELD.name: B-VHypC
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? HyperLEDA total apparent corrected B-V colour index

FIELD.name: a/b
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Ratio of the semi-major and semi-minor axes measured in 2MASS K

FIELD.name: PAGWGC
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? GWGC position angle (from north through east)

FIELD.name: Bmag2MPZ
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? 2MPZ apparent B magnitude (predicted if Flag not 0)
